        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hans', 3: 'We never understood how the Red Tide appeared. We only knew that it\\'d show up near a powerful Hetero-Creature, which was why Babylonia could tackle the Red Tide problem by taking down the Polyphage and Siren.', 4: '1'}"
